Sao Tome Awards Nigeria’s Oranto Oil License, Reuters Says

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-05-05T12:19:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/sao-tome-awards-nigeria-s-oranto-oil-license-reuters-says.html
Sao Tome and Principe has awarded
Oranto Petroleum Ltd., a Nigerian oil company, exploration
rights for a block in the country’s exclusive zone,  Reuters 
reported, citing a statement from the state-owned oil agency.  Block 3 covers 4,228 square kilometers (1,632 miles) and is
the first of the seven blocks in Sao Tome’s exclusive zone to be
awarded, the news agency reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mkhululi Mancotywa in Johannesburg at 
 mmancotywa1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Amanda Jordan at   ajordan11@bloomberg.net  